{"tid":2241613,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【12港人】謝偉俊上節目指願幫助，鏡頭後嚇鄒家成「遲早拉埋你」","createTime":"2020-10-13T12:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T12:47:13.000Z","uid":250654,"like":342,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"424383c0b11833308e5828c9df4f8820b7da3721","tid":2241613,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"【12港人】謝偉俊上節目指願幫助 鏡頭後嚇鄒家成「遲早拉埋你」<br />\n建制派立法會議員謝偉俊及鄒家成於今（13）日一同出席港台節目「視點31」，就12名港人涉嫌因「偷越國境罪」被拘留於中國一事作出討論。謝偉俊多次表示，被拘捕的人士需要承認自己在「本質上有問題」，要理解畏罪潛逃是「罪有應得」，但又指若家屬願意，會「盡力幫助」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然而鄒家成之後表示，<strong><span class=\"red\">謝偉俊在節目錄製結束後向他表示「你哋啲咁嘅提供協助嘅人，『遲早拉埋你』。」</span></strong><br />\n詳細報導內容: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H0p09G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H0p09G&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=e56965de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H0p09G</a><br />\n#DBC #DBChannel #加山傳播 #香港 #抗爭 #save12hkyouths"},{"pid":"e43d88a0534063276276cd7f8ead4527914015fa","tid":2241613,"uid":250654,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"呢個page d新聞都做得好好，希望大家可以click入去睇俾個like<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加山傳播<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdbchannel.hk%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=5a7c8a15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"ae251caef7e3c5e391a6816a29d10e35d03859a7","tid":2241613,"uid":250654,"like":169,"dislike":0,"score":169,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:04:12.000Z","msg":"謝偉俊同何妖都係仆街"},{"pid":"74f435e56eb4a38f8fa20b0a60714b3a89ade761","tid":2241613,"uid":186997,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"你呢啲咁嘅支那走狗，『遲早制裁埋你』"},{"pid":"b8268b90e27fae0d0ca2db2